item.title: Well this will be fun :D
item.dc:creator: @abatssk8ter abatssk8ter
item.description:
@abatssk8ter wrote:

oh well heres an idea for a “pure” not exactly a pure but a legit ass pker!

CombatLevel:94 (Maxed out)

Attack:60 (for wielding the dragon claws)

Strength:88 (combined with a super strength the dragon claws damage will be extensive :p)

Defence:70 (awesome stat to use barrows to destroy pures)

Constitution:80 (Decent health of course)

Magic:94 (For Vengeance)

Prayer:75 (Maybe 95 for turmoil eventualy :P)

Ranged:99 (Hit nice and high with your msb)

With these stats you can easily have a pretty good range tank with a combo deadly dragon claws and vengeance, heres my theory. Use a MSB as main weapon with a torags helmet and rune skirt with black dhide body, glory, snake boots, recoil ring, avas etc. with the magic shortbow you can use in combo with the vengeance! This will make it hard for the other person to use vengeance efficiently on you because you’re using a msb and they hit very rapid with not high, but not low attacks like 14s-20s etc this will drain there hp very fast with you using vengeance with it, when they’re low on health switch on your dragon claws and piety for a deadly kill switch and boom dead, no doubt about it.

Think it over, probably the best pker i could ever think of.
